<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b><font size="2">Introducing TaskPad<br>
  </font></b><font size="2">TaskPad is a simple application for keeping yourself 
  and others organized. Time management can often be a challenge, and with busy 
  lives sometimes we just forget to do even the simple things, like pick up the 
  milk on the way home. Now, as you shut down your PC before you leave the office, 
  TaskPad will be there to remind you. It sits on top of your desktop while not 
  getting in the way of your work. You can organize your tasks in outline style 
  or use different font styles to draw your attention to more important tasks. 
  And, TaskPad is so small and simple you won't have a hard time using it.</font></font></p>
